The remote robot acts on commands from the local robot and translates these instructions into physical actions by replicating the operator’s movements within the operational environment. The system uses a PD controller for unilateral position-position teleoperation to synchronise joints movements as formulated in (2):2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
