				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\dot{\theta }_{i,j}$$\end{document} is the angular velocity of the jth joint at the ith time point.

